程序包 projecttwo

类 FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
FitnessClass is the class that defines a fitness class the member can check in. In this project, we just assume there are only.
作者:
Michael Israel, Kangwei Zhu

    • FitnessClass

      public FitnessClass(String fitnessClassName, String instructorName, Time classTime, MemberDatabase memberDb, FitnessClass[] fitnessClasses)
      Initialize a newly created FitnessClass object.
      参数:
      fitnessClassName - The name of fitness class.
      instructorName - The name of instructor.
      classTime - The time of this fitness class.
      memberDb - The main memberDB that stores every fitness class's membership.
      fitnessClasses - The array that store all the FitnessClass object in this project.

    • isRegistered

      public boolean isRegistered(Member member)
      Check whether a member is checked in this fitness class or not.
      参数:
      member - A specific Member object that are going to be checked whether has checked in this course or not.
      返回:
      True if it is checked in, otherwise false.

    • isExpired

      public boolean isExpired(Member member)
      Check whether a member's membership has expired or not.
      参数:
      member - A specific Member object that going to be check if his membership has expired.
      返回:
      True if it is expired, false otherwise.

    • isTimeConflict

      private boolean isTimeConflict(String className, FitnessClass[] fitnessClasses, Member member)
      Check if the course that a member want to check in has time conflict with the other courses that this member choose.
      参数:
      className - The name of the class that this member want to check in.
      fitnessClasses - The array of FitnessClass object that store all fitnessclasses' information in this project.
      member - A specific Member object that going to check in.
      返回:
      True if there is a time confict, false if there is no time conflict.

    • isClassExist

      private boolean isClassExist(String className)
      Check whether a fitness class exist.
      参数:
      className - The name of the fitness class that you want check
      返回:
      True if the class exist. False if not exist.

    • checkIn

      public void checkIn(Member member, String className, FitnessClass[] fitnessClasses, MemberDatabase memberDb)
      Make a Member object check in this fitness class, and print the commandline messages.
      参数:
      member - A specific Member object that need to be check in this class.
      className - The name of the class that this member wants to check in.
      fitnessClasses - The array of all fitness classes that are available in this project.
      memberDb - The main member database that stores all the members in all fitness classes.

    • drop

      public void drop(Member member, MemberDatabase memberDb)
      Make a member drop from this fitness class.
      参数:
      member - A specific Member object that need to drop from this class.
      memberDb - The main member database that stores all the members in all fitness classes.
